name: S11_PID_05_BatteryMaxTemperature
description: Maximum temperature of the vehicle's battery pack.

name: S11_PID_05_BatteryMinTemperature
description: Minimum temperature of the vehicle's battery pack.

name: S11_PID_05_BatteryModule6Temperature
description: Temperature of the 6th module within the battery pack.

name: S11_PID_05_BatteryModule7Temperature
description: Temperature of the 7th module within the battery pack.

name: S11_PID_05_BatteryModule8Temperature
description: Temperature of the 8th module within the battery pack.

name: S11_PID_05_BatteryModule9Temperature
description: Temperature of the 9th module within the battery pack.

name: S11_PID_05_BatteryModule10Temperature
description: Temperature of the 10th module within the battery pack.

name: S11_PID_05_AvailableChargePower
description: The maximum power available for charging the battery.

name: S11_PID_05_AvailableDischargePower
description: The maximum power available for discharging the battery.

name: S11_PID_05_BatteryCellVoltageDeviation
description: The deviation or difference in voltage between individual cells within the battery pack

name: S11_PID_05_QuickChargeNormalStatus
description: The status indicating whether the quick charging feature is functioning normally.

name: S11_PID_05_AirbagH/wireDuty
description: The duty cycle or control signal for the airbag hardware.

name: S11_PID_05_BatteryHeaterTemp1
description: The temperature readings from two different battery heater sensors.

name: S11_PID_05_BatteryHeaterTemp2
description: The temperature readings from two different battery heater sensors.

name: S11_PID_05_StateofHealth(SOH)/MaxDeterioration
description: The overall health or maximum deterioration level of the battery pack.

name: S11_PID_05_MaxDeteriorationCellno.
description: The identification number of the cell within the battery pack that has the highest deterioration level.

name: S11_PID_05_MinDeterioration
description: The minimum deterioration level among all cells in the battery pack.

name: S11_PID_05_MinDeteriorationCellno.
description: The identification number of the cell within the battery pack that has the lowest deterioration level.

name: S11_PID_05_StateofCharge(SOC)Display
description: The current state of charge of the battery displayed to the user or driver.
